      "body" : "I thought double spaces between sentences were part of Satoshi's original vision :)\r\n\r\nWith that said: if we are to deviate from Satoshi's original vision with regards to spacing I suggest doing this change exhaustively:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ git grep -E 'LogPrintf*\\(.*?\".*?\\.  [a-zA-Z].*?\"'\r\nsrc/init.cpp:        LogPrintf(\"Block pruning enabled.  Use RPC call pruneblockchain(height) to manually prune block and undo files.\\n\");\r\nsrc/rpc/blockchain.cpp:        LogPrint(BCLog::RPC, \"Attempt to prune blocks close to the tip.  Retaining the minimum number of blocks.\\n\");\r\n```\r\n\r\nRegardless: welcome as a contributor @JetDeveloping! :)",
